      ],
      "cefrLevel": "C1",
      "idiomUsageNote": "该结构常用于日常消费、生活规划或职场建议等场景。通过与假设的‘原本情况（otherwise would）’对比，委婉、地道地突出某种方法、窍门或选择所带来的高性价比或高效率，非常符合母语者的口语思维习惯。",
      "englishDefinition": "To perform an action to a greater or better degree (such as more cheaply, effectively, or easily) than would be possible or expected under standard or normal circumstances."
    }
