    "wordIndex": 21,
    "wordText": "cleats",
    "category": "vocab",
    "sentenceContext": "You know, not worrying whether or not I can pay my mortgage or buy the groceries or if the kids need cleats, because we have a sports account, and that's the one that's going to pay for the cleats. 这样我就不用担心房贷、买菜的钱，或者孩子需要买足球鞋，因为这些都有各自独立的预算。⭐ mortgage 房贷｜cleats （足球等运动）钉鞋",
