    "customLemma": "dietitian",
    "sentenceContext": "HERNANDEZ: Right. And there are ways to do this. So registered dietitian Amy Lawson told me that she encourages people to build their restaurant meals around protein and fiber. Those are the things that will kind of keep you full. 当然有办法。注册营养师 Amy Lawson 告诉我，她建议大家点餐时以蛋白质和膳食纤维为核心（build… around），因为这些食物更有饱腹感。⭐ registered dietitian 注册营养师｜build… around… 围绕……来安排（⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 很好迁移）｜protein and fiber 蛋白质和膳食纤维｜keep you full 让你更有饱腹感",
