    "category": "idiom",
    "customLemma": "hit all the categories",
    "sentenceContext": "And it can be hard to actually get that balance if you're ordering something like a soup or a chili, where you don't really have control over that ratio, like a half to a quarter to a quarter, just making sure you're hitting all those categories of non-starchy vegetables, protein and complex carbs will help you. 不过，如果你点的是汤或者辣炖菜这类食物，就很难真正做到这种比例，因为你没法控制各种食材的占比。不过，只要确保这一餐包含了非淀粉类蔬菜、蛋白质和复合碳水这几个类别，就已经很不错了。⭐ have control over 控制；掌握（高频）｜ratio 比例（B2）｜hit all the categories 覆盖所有类别（很自然）",
