    "wordText": "hunger hormones are ... loud",
    "category": "idiom",
    "customLemma": "hunger hormones are ... loud",
    "sentenceContext": "AMY LAWSON: Especially when we go to a restaurant, and we get there, and we are really hungry - our hunger hormones are really loud, and they are telling us, I want - give me all the carbohydrates, give me the simple things, give me the quickest source of fuel. 尤其是当我们到了餐厅，已经非常饿的时候，饥饿激素（hunger hormones）会变得特别活跃，它们仿佛一直在对我们喊：\"我要碳水！我要最简单的食物！我要最快能提供能量的东西！\"⭐ hunger hormones 饥饿激素｜the quickest source of fuel 最快的能量来源",
    "startTime": 663.655,
    "reviewCount": 0,
    "dateAdded": "2026-07-04T03:40:50.549Z"
  },
