    "wordText": "commenters",
    "category": "vocab",
    "customLemma": "commenter",
    "sentenceContext": "And then commenters were a little bit split on whether to just make a meal of side dishes and appetizers to save money or to skip side dishes and appetizers and just order entrees to save money, but it seems like people do both of those strategies. 另外，网友们对此意见不太一致。有些人觉得可以只点配菜和前菜来省钱；也有人认为应该直接点主菜、跳过前菜和配菜。看起来，两种做法都有人采用。⭐ be split on 在某件事上意见不一致（C1）｜side dish 配菜｜appetizer 前菜｜entrée 主菜",
