    "sentenceContext": "Beijing to London, I'd love to bring those stalls with, like, hot peanuts and, like, snacks and traditional Chinese pancakes.",
    "sentenceTranslation": "如果是从北京带到伦敦，我最想把那些卖热花生、小吃和中式煎饼的小摊一起搬过去。",
    "sentenceVocab": "⭐ food stall｜traditional Chinese pancakes",
    "startTime": 393.589,
    "reviewCount": 1,
    "dateAdded": "2026-07-08T09:13:05.910Z",
    "translationCache": {
      "lemma": "stall",
