        "with toes turned in"
      ],
      "cefrLevel": "",
      "idiomUsageNote": "",
      "englishDefinition": "",
      "patternPractice": [
        {
          "chinese": "在瑜伽课上，老师让我们双脚内扣以更好地拉伸大腿内侧。",
          "english": "In yoga class, the teacher asked us to turn our toes in to better stretch (stretch out) the inner thighs.",
