        },
        {
          "chinese": "物理治疗师建议他走路时轻微内扣双脚，以减轻膝盖压力。",
          "english": "The physical therapist advised him to slightly turn his toes in while walking to alleviate (ease up) the pressure on his knees.",
          "difficulty": "高级"
        },
        {
          "chinese": "在普拉提动作中，双脚内扣有助于激活核心肌群。",
