    "sentenceContext": "I ended up speaking with Erewhon about potentially doing this smoothie collab that was around the same time as the Rhode launch, so it kind of coincided and went together.",
    "sentenceTranslation": "后来我和 Erewhon 商量合作推出这款奶昔，时间刚好和 Rhode 上市差不多，所以两件事就自然配合到一起了。",
    "sentenceVocab": "⭐ end up doing —— 最终做了……｜potentially —— 有可能地｜collab —— 合作（collaboration）｜coincide —— 同时发生；巧合地重合",
