    "wordText": "I spy",
    "category": "idiom",
    "customLemma": "I spy ...",
    "sentenceContext": "Okay, this one says, \"What sweets did you get? I spy Haribo.\"",
    "sentenceTranslation": "好，这条评论说：\"你买了哪些零食？我看到 Haribo 了。\"",
    "sentenceVocab": "⭐ I spy… —— 我看到……了（口语）",
    "startTime": 255.415,
