    "translationCache": {
      "lemma": "i spy",
      "ipa": "/aɪ spaɪ/",
      "translation": "（儿童游戏用语）我发现了……；我看见……",
      "pronunciationGuide": "注意 'I' 发长元音 /aɪ/，'spy' 中 'sp' 不送气，/aɪ/ 与 /aɪ/ 相同，整体连读自然。",
      "collocations": "I spy with my little eye; play I spy; I spy game",
      "cefrLevel": "A2",
      "idiomUsageNote": "",
      "englishDefinition": "used in a children's game where one player says 'I spy with my little eye something beginning with...' and others guess the object; also used informally to indicate that one has noticed or spotted something.",
      "patternPractice": [
        {
          "chinese": "在长途汽车旅行中，孩子们玩“我看见”游戏来打发时间。",
          "english": "During the long bus trip, the kids played 'I spy' to pass the time.",
