    "wordText": "edging to",
    "category": "vocab",
    "customLemma": "edge to",
    "sentenceContext": "My whole family holding hands in a 360, edging to where we hoped the house was.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;I want to go home!&nbsp;",
    "sentenceTranslation": "我们全家手牵着手围成一圈，小心翼翼地一点一点挪向我们希望是房子的方向。 我要回家！",
    "sentenceVocab": "⭐ edge towards… —— 小心翼翼地慢慢挪向……｜hold hands —— 牵手（💡这里 edge 是非常好的 C1 动词，表示\"缓慢、谨慎地移动\"。）",
    "startTime": 120.725,
    "reviewCount": 0,
    "dateAdded": "2026-07-17T03:23:28.877Z",
    "translationCache": {
      "lemma": "edge to",
      "ipa": "/ɛdʒ tuː/",
      "translation": "（缓慢谨慎地）向…移动",
      "pronunciationGuide": "",
      "collocations": [
        "edge to the door",
        "edge to the front",
        "edge to safety",
        "edge to the side"
      ],
      "cefrLevel": "",
      "idiomUsageNote": "",
      "englishDefinition": "",
      "patternPractice": [
        {
          "chinese": "在浓雾中，我们小心翼翼地朝悬崖边缘移动。",
          "english": "In the thick fog, we carefully edged to the cliff's edge."
        },
        {
          "chinese": "她穿过拥挤的房间，慢慢朝出口移动。",
          "english": "She edged to the exit through the crowded room."
        },
        {
          "chinese": "随着风暴加剧，他们缓慢地朝避难所移动。",
          "english": "As the storm intensified, they slowly edged to the shelter."
        },
        {
          "chinese": "谈判陷入僵局，双方都谨慎地朝妥协方案移动。",
          "english": "The negotiations were deadlocked, and both sides cautiously edged to a compromise."
        }
      ]
    },
    "teacherExplanation": "**1. 中式英语 vs 地道表达**  \n你第一反应可能是“move towards”或“walk to”，但**edge to**不是普通移动，而是**小心翼翼、试探性地挪动**，像在黑暗中摸墙走。中式英语常忽略这种“谨慎感”，直接说“go to”就丢了灵魂。  \n\n**2. 学术深度分析**  \n*Edge*作动词本义是“给…加边”，引申为**缓慢、侧身移动**，常带**焦虑或不确定**色彩。这里一家人手拉手形成360度圈，**edging to**房子——画面感极强：不是大步流星，而是像螃蟹一样横着蹭，生怕走散。感情色彩：**戏谑中带点辛酸**，像在玩恐怖版“丢手绢”。  \n\n**3. 趣味记忆**  \n想象你**edge**（边缘）上有个**edge**（优势）——但这里**edge**是动词，像在悬崖边**蹭**着走。谐音梗：**“挨挤”**——一家人挨着挤着挪向家，完美！"
  },
  {
    "id": "github-cloud-The_Terrifying_Difference_Between_Night_And_Day_In_The_Countryside_Michael_McIntyre-26-1-1784258691069",
    "materialId": "github-cloud-The_Terrifying_Difference_Between_Night_And_Day_In_The_Countryside_Michael_McIntyre",
