    "sentenceVocab": "⭐ put somebody on —— 把电话转给某人（电话用语）",
    "startTime": 277.462,
    "reviewCount": 0,
    "dateAdded": "2026-07-17T03:33:02.231Z",
    "translationCache": {
      "lemma": "put someone on",
      "ipa": "/pʊt ˈsʌmwʌn ɒn/",
      "translation": "让某人接电话；戏弄某人",
      "pronunciationGuide": "",
      "collocations": "put someone on hold, put someone on speaker, put someone on the spot",
      "cefrLevel": "",
      "idiomUsageNote": "",
      "englishDefinition": "",
      "patternPractice": [
        {
          "chinese": "你能帮我接通销售部经理吗？",
          "english": "Can you put me through to the sales manager?"
        },
        {
          "chinese": "别信他的话，他只是在戏弄你。",
          "english": "Don't believe him; he's just putting you on."
        },
        {
          "chinese": "请稍等，我马上让他接电话。",
          "english": "Please hold on; I'll put him on right away."
        },
